videos.description: Gonzaga catches North Carolina sleeping on defense as Josh Perkins finds Rui Hachimura for a dunk.
videos.headline: Hachimura flushes two-handed dunk

videos.description: North Carolina's Cameron Johnson hauls in an offensive rebound and charges to the cup for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Johnson flies through the lane for jam

videos.description: Leaky Black comes up with a steal and throws down a two-handed dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Black steal leads to fast-break dunk

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. finishes the Gonzaga fast break with a reverse layup.
videos.headline: Norvell Jr. swoops in for reverse layup

videos.description: Cameron Johnson gets the Gonzaga defender off balance and knocks down a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Johnson drains step back 3-ball
